        <h1 class="entry-title"><a href="/blog/2012/10/28/english-phonetics-keyboard-layout-for-mac-os-x/">English Phonetics Keyboard Layout for Mac OS X</a></h1>
      
    
    
      <p class="meta">
        








  


<time datetime="2012-10-28T23:13:00+08:00" pubdate data-updated="true">Oct 28<span>th</span>, 2012</time>
        
         | <a href="/blog/2012/10/28/english-phonetics-keyboard-layout-for-mac-os-x/#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
        
      </p>
    
  </header>


  <div class="entry-content"><p>前几天写了个TextMate Bundle，用来输入国际音标的HTML Entities，托管在github: <a href="https://github.com/xiaolai/ipa-html-entities-tmbundle">ipa-html-entities-tmbundle</a>。后来发现鼠须管有一个IPA Schema，不过，用过之后，发现对于只需要输入英语音标的需求来说，并不是很方便。</p>

<p>今天花了十几分钟，用<a href="http://scripts.sil.org/cms/scripts/page.php?site_id=nrsi&amp;id=ukelele">Ukelele</a>编写了一个<a href="http://www.lixiaolai.com/files/English-Phonetics.keylayout">English Phonetics Keyboard Layout</a>(点击鼠标右键选择‘另存为…’)。下载之后，放进 <code>/Library/Keyboard Layouts/</code> 目录，而后就可以像添加输入法一样调用了：</p>

<p><img class="center" src="http://www.lixiaolai.com/images/input-sources.png" /></p>

<p>键盘布局如下：</p>

<p><img class="center" src="http://www.lixiaolai.com/images/epk.png" /></p>

<p><img class="center" src="http://www.lixiaolai.com/images/epk-shift.png" /></p>

</div>
  
  


